## Typography

```scss
// Stack: modern system fonts with CJK fallbacks
--font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
               'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;

// Scale
--font-size-xs: 0.7rem    // Metadata, badges, tiny labels
--font-size-sm: 0.78rem   // Secondary text, list items
--font-size-md: 0.875rem  // Body text, input, message bubbles
--font-size-base: 1rem    // Base (rarely used directly)

// Weights
--font-weight-normal: 400
--font-weight-medium: 500
--font-weight-semibold: 600

// Line heights
--line-height-tight: 1.4    // Headings, labels
--line-height-base: 1.6     // UI text
--line-height-relaxed: 1.75 // Message content, paragraphs
```

**Rules:**
- Prefer `--font-size-sm` (0.78rem) for sidebar/panel text
- Prefer `--font-size-md` (0.875rem) for main content and chat bubbles
- Never go below `--font-size-xs` (0.7rem) for readable content
- Use `font-weight: 600` only for section titles and active states

---

## Spacing Scale

```scss
--space-1: 0.25rem   // Tight gaps (between tags, badge padding)
--space-2: 0.5rem    // Small (button padding vertical, list item gap)
--space-3: 0.75rem   // Medium (card padding, section gap)
--space-4: 1rem      // Standard (component padding)
--space-5: 1.25rem   // Large (section separation)
--space-6: 1.5rem    // XL (main content horizontal padding)
```

**Rules:**
- Sidebar internal padding: `var(--space-4)`
- Chat messages horizontal padding: `var(--space-6)`
- Between messages gap: `var(--space-4)`
- Input row padding: `var(--space-3) var(--space-4)`

---

## Border Radius

```scss
--radius-sm: 4px    // Small buttons, badges, filter chips
--radius-md: 8px    // Standard buttons, inputs, small cards
--radius-lg: 12px   // Message bubbles, panels, cards
--radius-xl: 16px   // Large modals/drawers
--radius-pill: 9999px // Tags, pill buttons, scrollbar thumbs
```

**Rules:**
- Message bubbles: `--radius-lg`
- Action buttons: `--radius-md`
- Filter/type badges: `--radius-pill`
- Panel cards: `--radius-lg`

---

## Shadows

```scss
--shadow-sm: 0 1px 3px rgba(44, 40, 32, 0.06), 0 1px 2px rgba(44, 40, 32, 0.04)
--shadow-md: 0 4px 12px rgba(44, 40, 32, 0.08), 0 2px 4px rgba(44, 40, 32, 0.04)
```

**Rules:**
- Use `--shadow-sm` on message bubbles, active tab indicators
- Use `--shadow-md` on modals, overlays, detail panels
- Prefer shadows over borders for depth — not both
- Never use `box-shadow` with pure black (`rgba(0,0,0,...)`) — always use warm dark base `rgba(44,40,32,...)`

---

## Transitions

```scss
--transition-fast: 0.15s ease   // Hover states, button feedback
--transition-base: 0.2s ease    // Tab switches, panel reveals
```

---

## Layout

```scss
--sidebar-width: 320px
```

**Rules:**
- Layout: `display: flex; height: 100vh` — sidebar + main flex row
- Sidebar: fixed width, `overflow: hidden`, `flex-direction: column`
- Main content: `flex: 1; min-width: 0; overflow: auto`
- Never use `100%` width on flex children without `min-width: 0`
- Use `CSS Grid` for 2D layouts (card grids, form layouts)
- Use `Flexbox` for 1D layouts (rows, columns, alignment)

---

## Component Patterns

### Buttons

Three variants only:

```scss
// Primary — main actions (Send, Save)
.btn--primary {
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: #fff;
  border: none;
  padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  &:hover { background: var(--color-primary-hover); }
}

// Ghost — secondary actions (Summarize, Update Persona)
.btn--ghost {
  background: var(--color-surface);
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  &:hover { background: var(--color-bg); color: var(--color-text); }
}

// Success — confirm/adopt actions
.btn--success {
  background: var(--color-success);
  color: #fff;
  border: none;
}

// Size modifier
.btn--sm { padding: calc(var(--space-1) + 2px) var(--space-3); font-size: var(--font-size-xs); }

// Disabled — always
&:disabled { opacity: 0.45; cursor: not-allowed; }
```

### Inputs & Textareas

```scss
textarea, input[type="text"] {
  font-family: var(--font-family);
  font-size: var(--font-size-md);
  color: var(--color-text);
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  padding: var(--space-3);
  transition: border-color var(--transition-fast);

  &:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(92, 103, 242, 0.1);
  }
  &::placeholder { color: var(--color-text-muted); }
}
```

### Tab Bar (Pill Switcher)

```scss
.tab-bar {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-1);
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  padding: var(--space-1);

  button {
    flex: 1;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);

    &.active {
      background: var(--color-surface);
      color: var(--color-text);
      font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
  }
}
```

### Notification Bars

```scss
// Sit flush at the top of the content area — no margin, full width
.notification {
  padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
  font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;

  &--error { color: var(--color-error); background: var(--color-error-bg); border-color: var(--color-error-border); }
  &--success { color: var(--color-success); background: var(--color-success-bg); border-color: var(--color-success-border); }
}
```

### Scrollbars

Always style scrollbars to be minimal and warm:

```scss
@mixin custom-scrollbar {
  &::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
  &::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
  &::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  }
}
```

