## SCSS File Structure

```
frontend/src/
  styles/
    _variables.scss   # :root CSS custom properties — single source of truth
    _mixins.scss      # Reusable SCSS mixins (custom-scrollbar, btn-base, flex-row)
    _base.scss        # CSS reset, body, box-sizing, font smoothing
  styles.scss         # @use all partials — imported by Angular globally
```

**Rules:**
- All color/space/radius values MUST be in `_variables.scss`
- Component SCSS files use `var(--token-name)` — never hardcode values
- Mixins are shared by importing: `@use 'src/styles/mixins' as *` in component SCSS
- `styles.scss` is the only file Angular includes globally — all partials go through it

